#: ../../geovista/docs/src/generated/gallery/grid/reykjanes_contour.rst:29
msgid ""
"The sample data is taken from a Met Office NAME Model time-series simulation"
" of the Icelandic Reykjanes Peninsula eruption on 29 May 2024."
msgstr ""

#: ../../geovista/docs/src/generated/gallery/grid/reykjanes_contour.rst:32
msgid ""
"A structured grid of cubic voxels is constructed for the 1D spatial "
"coordinates and then thresholded to reveal the underlying volcanic plume of "
"Sulphur Dioxide Air Concentration."
msgstr ""

#: ../../geovista/docs/src/generated/gallery/grid/reykjanes_contour.rst:36
msgid ""
"The visualization is enhanced by rendering isosufaces of the plume using a "
"mixture of opacity and smooth shading to yield a semi-transparent cloud-like"
" effect."
msgstr ""

#: ../../geovista/docs/src/generated/gallery/grid/reykjanes_contour.rst:40
msgid ""
"The cited release location of the eruption on the peninsula is marked, "
"highlighting the volcanic plume's eastward transport and southerly "
"dispersion."
msgstr ""

